										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Crypto exchange choices are difficult; platforms claim the best fees, tokens, and safety. MEXC, active since 2018, grows globally. Many now ask: Is MEXC a safe crypto exchange? In this MEXC review, we’ll take a closer look at the exchange’s security measures, user experience, supported assets, and overall reliability to help you decide if it’s the right platform for your trading needs this March.</span></p>
