<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To get started, create your MEXC account. Simply visit the </span><a href="https://www.mexc.com/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">MEXC website</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and click on “Sign Up” located in the top right corner. The signup process is pretty straightforward and won’t take long at all. You can register using your email or your mobile number. </span></p>
