<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When you start trading on MEXC, it usually takes place in the spot market, where you can buy and sell digital assets such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, and many other tokens. As soon as you access the trading interface, you’ll find real-time price charts, an order book, and tools that help you place different kinds of orders. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For those interested in more advanced trading options, MEXC also provides futures trading, enabling you to trade contracts based on cryptocurrency prices. Above all, it’s essential to keep risk management as a key part of your strategy.</span></p>
