<p data-start="269" data-end="536">Moreover, Vertcoin allows anyone to mine VTC coins right from home. With any compatible CPU or GPU device, users can easily start mining $VERT. In addition, setting up Vertcoin mining is simple and beginner-friendly, which makes it even more appealing to newcomers.</p>
<p data-start="538" data-end="988" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">From a technical perspective, Vertcoin uses the Lyra2REv3 mining mechanism — an advanced form of proof-of-work. As a result, it operates more efficiently than Bitcoin, with a new block mined every 2.5 minutes. Furthermore, the current reward rate of 12.5 VTC per block makes it a profitable coin to mine. However, a halving event scheduled for June 2026 will reduce the block reward to 6.25 VTC, potentially affecting long-term mining incentives.</p>
