<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This tournament features a redesigned point calculation system that places a heavier structural emphasis on early market activity via the </span><b>Early Bird Boost Multiplier</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Trading earlier in the weekly window significantly amplifies your baseline score using this direct text-based equation:</span></p>
