<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Rising Trader Score component:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 5,000 (Capped Limit) * 1.2 = 6,000 USDT</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Final Day 1 Effective Volume:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 20,000 + 6,000 = </span><b>26,000 USDT</b></li>
