<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Following Day 1, User A&#8217;s $5,000 boost cap is entirely depleted. For the remainder of the promotion round, they will no longer receive the 1.2x Rising Trader bonus, though they retain full eligibility to utilize the standard Early Bird multiplier table.</span></p>
